DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you
	 purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Ti
	ckets\nResale Tickets \nVon Decarlo LIVE at Punch Line Irving\nDon’t miss 
	Von Decarlo as she brings her bold\, unapologetic stand-up comedy to Punch
	 Line Irving on Wednesday\, July 1\, 2026. Known for her fearless humor an
	d magnetic stage presence\, Von Decarlo delivers a show packed with laughs
	\, real talk\, and unforgettable moments. \nEvent Details\nDate: Wednesday
	\, July 1\, 2026\nTime: 7:30 PM CDT\nVenue: Punch Line Irving\nAddress: 31
	0 W Las Colinas Blvd.\, Suite 130\, Irving\, TX 75039\nAge Requirement: 18
	+ (valid government-issued photo ID required)\nMinimum: 2-beverage minimum
	 per person \nAbout Von Decarlo\nVon Decarlo is a rising stand-up comedian
	 and social media sensation known for her candid\, hilarious takes on rela
	tionships\, life\, and pop culture. With a massive following on TikTok and
	 Instagram\, she has built a devoted fanbase who love her no-filter approa
	ch to comedy. Her live shows are an extension of her authentic\, laugh-out
	-loud personality. \nWhat to Expect\n\nBold\, unapologetic stand-up comedy
	\nHilarious takes on relationships and everyday life\nIntimate comedy club
	 atmosphere at Punch Line Irving\nFull bar and beverage service during the
	 show\n18+ event — bring valid government-issued photo ID\nLimited seating
	 — tickets selling fast\n\nVenue Information\nPunch Line Irving is the DFW
	 area’s newest premier comedy club\, located at 310 W Las Colinas Blvd.\, 
	Suite 130 in Irving\, Texas. The venue offers a full bar\, cashless paymen
	t\, and an intimate setting perfect for live stand-up comedy. \nTicket Inf
	ormation\nTickets start at $27.65 and are on sale now. Only 84 tickets rem
	aining — don’t wait! All sales are final. A 2-beverage minimum per person 
	applies. Doors open one hour before show time. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale 
	Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you 
	purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales ar
	e final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID required for entry. 
	18+ event.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/von-decarlo-live-at-punch-l
	ine-irving/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/von-decarlo-live-at-punch-line-irving/
LOCATION:Punch Line Irving\, 310 W Las Colinas Blvd.\, Suite 130\, Irving\,
	 TX\, 75039\, United States Of America
