SUMMARY:Mario Adrion LIVE at San Jose Improv
DTSTAMP:20260701T033028Z
DTSTART:20260701T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nAbout the Performer\nMario Adr
	ion is a stand-up comedian from a small town in Germany who has taken the 
	internet — and the world — by storm. With over 3.5 million followers acros
	s social media platforms\, Mario built his fanbase through refreshingly ho
	nest and self-deprecating comedy that resonates with audiences everywhere.
	 \nHis comedy is uniquely vulnerable\, playing with the struggles and ster
	eotypes of being a retired male model and a European navigating life in th
	e United States. Think fish-out-of-water humor with a sharp\, charming twi
	st — and a German accent that makes everything funnier. \nOver the past fe
	w years\, Mario has toured his wildly popular “The German EFiciency Tour” 
	around the world\, selling out shows across the US\, UK\, Europe\, and the
	 Middle East. He filmed his debut hour-long special in January 2026 and is
	 now embarking on an even bigger international tour\, “The Superior Comedy
	 Tour\,” performing in clubs and theaters across the globe. Based out of L
	os Angeles\, Mario Adrion is one of the hottest rising comics in the game 
	right now. \nEvent Details\n\nDate: Wednesday\, July 1\, 2026\nShow Time: 
	7:30 PM PDT (Doors open at 6:00 PM)\nVenue: San Jose Improv\, 62 S Second 
	St\, San Jose\, CA 95113\nAge Restriction: 21+ Event — Valid ID required a
	t the door\nContent: Stand-up comedy — clean\, relatable\, and hilarious\n
	\nAbout the Venue\nThe San Jose Improv is one of the Bay Area’s premier st
	and-up comedy clubs\, located in the heart of downtown San Jose at 62 S Se
	cond St. Part of the nationally renowned Improv comedy club chain\, the Sa
	n Jose Improv has hosted some of the biggest names in comedy and continues
	 to be the go-to destination for world-class stand-up in Silicon Valley. \
	nThe intimate club setting creates an electric atmosphere where every seat
	 feels close to the stage. The venue features a full-service bar and dinin
	g menu\, with a mandatory two-item minimum purchase per guest in the showr
	oom. Seating is general admission and first-come\, first-served (with the 
	exception of groups and premium booths)\, so arriving early is recommended
	 to secure the best spots. \nThe San Jose Improv is easily accessible in d
	owntown San Jose\, with multiple parking garages and public transit option
	s nearby. The venue’s cozy\, club-style layout ensures an up-close and per
	sonal comedy experience that larger theaters simply can’t match. \nWhat to
	 Expect\nExpect a night of sharp\, self-aware comedy that blends European 
	sensibility with American pop culture observations. Mario Adrion’s show is
	 a solo stand-up performance — no openers\, just Mario and his signature s
	torytelling style that has captivated millions online. \nHis material draw
	s heavily from his own life: the absurdity of being a former model\, the c
	ulture shock of moving from Germany to the US\, and the universal awkwardn
	ess of modern life. Fans of his social media content will recognize his st
	yle immediately — but live\, it hits on a completely different level. \nTh
	is is a 21+ event\, so bring your ID. The two-item minimum at the Improv m
	eans you’ll be sipping something while you laugh — which honestly just mak
	es the whole experience better. No phones\, no photography\, no recording 
	during the show. Just pure\, unfiltered comedy. \nTicket Information\nPric
	e Range: $25 – $90 (plus fees) \n\nGA Ticket: $25 (+ fees)\nVIP Ticket: $4
	0 (+ fees) — preferred seating\n\n\n\nOfficial TicketsResale Tickets \nThi
	s post contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at no extra cost
	 to you.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/mario-adrion-live-at-san-jose
	-improv/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/mario-adrion-live-at-san-jose-improv/
LOCATION:San Jose Improv\, 62 S Second St\, San Jose\, California\, 95113\,
	 United States
