SUMMARY:Wingman Wednesdays Miami’s Social Comedy Show
DTSTAMP:20260701T033028Z
DTSTART:20260701T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Blackbird Ordinary. Meet new people. Laugh at hilarious dating 
	stories. Join the conversation. Ladies drink free during showtime 9-10:30 
	PM.\n\n\nA fun night out where people happen to meet. \nWingman Wednesdays
	 is Miami’s social comedy show where dating\, relationships\, and modern r
	omance become the night’s entertainment. Hosted by Miami’s Best Comedian M
	anny Garavito and Miami’s Best Master of Ceremonies Luke Prince\, the show
	 stirs up live comedy\, tasteful crowd interaction\, audience stories\, te
	rrible dating advice\, red flags\, green flags\, first dates on the spot\,
	 and the hilarious realities of navigating Miami’s social scene. \nWhether
	 you’re single\, taken\, in the alphabet\, somewhere in between\, or just 
	here to watch the tea spill\, you’ll be part of a night filled with laughs
	\, unexpected moments\, and real conversations. Audience participation is 
	encouraged but never required\, making it just as fun to watch as it is to
	 jump in. \nBring your friends\, your situationships\, your worst dating s
	tories\, but most importantly your sense of humor. \nLadies drink free dur
	ing showtime from 9:00 PM to 10:30 PM. \nComedy. Cocktails. Questionable d
	ecisions. \nTopics include but are not limited to: \nBrickell finance bros
	 \nYacht season \nSugar daddy retirement plans \nInstagram followers \n“Wh
	at do you do?” stress tests \nPenthouse with air matresses \nDating apps \
	nGym culture \nPlastic surgery \nSpiritual girls \nHow to Ghost 101 \nToxi
	c Green Flags \n…And enough unsolicited dating advice to keep everyone sin
	gle a little longer. \nCome watch. Come participate. Or just sit back and 
	enjoy the turbulence. \nTicket Options \nGeneral Admission (FREE: frist co
	me\, first serve)First come\, first served. Whatever seats are not purchas
	ed will be available to anyone who arrives early. Once they’re gone\, they
	’re gone. \n$25 Guaranteed Seating + Wingmen for HireSkip the rush and sec
	ure your seats in advance. Plus\, you’ll be guaranteed an opportunity to j
	oin Manny and Luke on stage for live crowd interaction\, dating advice\, m
	atchmaking attempts\, relationship advice\, or whatever romantic turbulenc
	e the evening encounters. Limited spots available. \n$50 VIP Flight Crew E
	xperience (Guaranteed Seating\, Wingmen for Hire\, VIP Bottle Afterparty A
	ccess AND Merch)Everything included: guaranteed seating\, Wingman for hire
	\, access to our bottle section for the afterparty with Manny and Luke\, p
	lus exclusive Miami Comedy merch to take home. VERY Limited spots.\n\nhttp
	s://comedycalendar.com/event/wingman-wednesdays-miamis-social-comedy-show-
	3/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/wingman-wednesdays-miamis-social-comed
	y-show-3/
LOCATION:Blackbird Ordinary\, Southwest 1st Avenue 729\, Miami\, FL\, 33130
	\, United States
